title: 'A super knock' - Carey scores century to help Australia past 300
subtitle: Alex Carey stars for Australia on the opening day of the third Ashes Test, scoring 106, his third career Test century, and his first against England, to help Australia recover from 94-4 to 307-7 at stumps in Adelaide.
full_text: Alex Carey stars for Australia on the opening day of the third Ashes Test, scoring 106, his third career Test century, and his first against England, to help Australia recover from 94-4 to 307-7 at stumps in Adelaide.
